>  Modifying .cpanel.yml: If you ever need to add more folders to your exclusion list alongside vendor/mailjet/, remember to always edit the file on your local machine, commit it, and push it to GitHub first. Modifying it directly on the server via File Manager will cause cPanel to flag "uncommitted changes" [I0] and lock the deploy button again. The Golden Rule: Always pull before you deploy. 

